Package: nomadforms
Type: Package
Title: Offline-Capable Survey Platform for Field Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: An open-source, offline-capable survey data collection platform
    built on surveydown for field research in Low and Middle Income Countries.
    Provides visual survey builder, REDCap codebook import, mobile optimization,
    and rich data exports (Stata, SPSS, R).
